{"tid":1507537,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[世清入] 觀塘瑞和街現鏹水狂徒","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:11:57.000Z","uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a17a1c8a91835638fcc41872a5927d913dd3748","tid":1507537,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gbd8FRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbd8FRJ.jpg&h=d1c5bbe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發地點：官塘端和街市附近<br />\n事發時間：8月24 日晚上7:00<br />\n<br />\n剛剛有個痴線佬,響我鋪頭隔離嘅文具舖買咗兩支水槍，本身我都冇留意佢喺度搞緊啲乜嘢，點知過咗一陣，佢係咁fing自己隻手，嗰時我就見到有支鏹水係地下，嗰個人將啲鏹水放入玩具水槍入邊，嗰時佢自己整到自己，跟住我同阿姐入咗去文具舖同佢老細講，叫佢老細報警，個痴線佬之後走咗。<br />\n<br />\n個痴線佬着藍色Polo,米黃色短褲，40幾50歲中年男人，希望大家呼籲，正在發完夢嘅人，小心陌生人嘅手攞住嘅嘢，提防有意外發生。<br />\n<br />\n地下遺留兩支玩具水槍，但係支鏹水就唔見咗，大家日後要提防有可能會發生咁樣嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n#唔想再發生連儂隧道女記者嘅事<br />\n#大家小心d<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/670099089/posts/10157788050464090?s=100005592150866&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F670099089%2Fposts%2F10157788050464090%3Fs%3D100005592150866%26sfns%3Dmo&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=172c012e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/670099089/posts/10157788050464090?s=100005592150866&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"d877438f107003e0e0e90a51e3c24992ce9f2ae9","tid":1507537,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=00fd3b94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"2a9c1c61c1ba8bddb12a